snippet.title: [PSX] Digimon Digital Card Battle
snippet.description:
I can't believe that I found my 10-years old memory card saved data...
I played this game a lot long time ago... more than 10 years ago...
It's actually fun card game...

Trio Deck (vs. Apokarimon) = 3 partner cards, and the rest are option cards
U-Strength Deck (vs. BlackWarGreymon) = Occupied with Ultimate Cards and "Mutant Digivolve" cards, the rest are partner cards and some of option cards
